YOUR TRADITIONAL FAMILY BARBERS

Call for booking:

(405) 555-0128

Book Now

There are people who go beyond their activities and create something cool and exclusive, influencing the world around them and setting trends. Woodmart Hair & Beard has gathered just such people—the most talented masters of their craft.

Geoffrey Mott

Darron Kulikowski

Thad Eddings

Elmer Laverty

Pedro Huard

Darron Kulikowski

Daryl Nehls

STYLES & SERVICES

CLIPPER CUT

This is a quick and easy way to get a short, even haircut with scissors

BEARD TRIMMING

Beard looking its best, including trimming, shaping, and styling

MEN'S CUTS

We will give you a classic haircut or a more modern style

CHILDREN'S HAIRCUT

We know how to make the process fun and comfortable for everyone

HAIRCUTS

Men’s haircut

$48.00 Haircut (help in choosing a style based on external characteristics)

Beard trimming

$30.00 Beard haircut and styling

Haircut + Beard

$65.00 Complex haircut (style selection, styling recommendations)

Children’s haircut up to 10 years

$35.00 Children’s haircut (performed mainly with scissors)

SHAVING

Royal shave

$25.00 Royal Shave with a dangerous razor

Head shave

$25.00 Head shave with a dangerous razor

ADDITIONAL SERVICES

Camouflage of gray beard

$20.00 Toning of gray hair of the beard

Camouflage of gray hair

$25.00 Toning of gray hair of the head

Camouflage gray complex

$35.00 Toning of gray beard and head in the complex

Hair styling

$10.00 Performed with a hair dryer and comb Book Now
